739
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,000
Siapa Jiang Mengmeng?

740
00:34:18,120 --> 00:34:19,200
Seseorang bernama Tuan Murong…

741
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,520
memintaku memberikan ini padamu.

742
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,040
Tuan Murong?

743
00:34:23,200 --> 00:34:23,960
Murong Chen.

744
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:26,490
(Sudah ada petunjuk tentang Bunga
Kembang Malam.Tunggu kami di kedai teh.)

745
00:34:26,640 --> 00:34:27,360
Mengmeng.

746
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,400
Apa yang tertulis di dalamnya?

747
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:31,560
Dia bilang, dia dan Chang Kong
sudah menemukan petunjuk.

748
00:34:31,720 --> 00:34:33,040
Kita diminta ke kedai teh.

749
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:34,680
Kedai teh?

750
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,720
Kenapa mereka
tak datang sendiri mencari kita?

751
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:41,280
